    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">
        <strong>20 May 1947</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">Volume 437</div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
        <div class="container">
            <div id="debateContent">
                <div class="highlightedSearchTerms"></div>
                <div class="content-container">


<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-86c2b84b-69f7-43bb-b498-311988453851'>
            
<p class="">88.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-bfd04c1e-a02a-4d3b-a5e0-6237a1203860">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-bfd04c1e-a02a-4d3b-a5e0-6237a1203860">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-bfd04c1e-a02a-4d3b-a5e0-6237a1203860">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-bfd04c1e-a02a-4d3b-a5e0-6237a1203860">
                Mr. Sydney Silverman
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-bfd04c1e-a02a-4d3b-a5e0-6237a1203860" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-05-20/debates/67474fbf-3ef4-4bab-8db5-4636ce46ab04/Aliens#contribution-bfd04c1e-a02a-4d3b-a5e0-6237a1203860">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Minister of Labour whether he is yet in a position to make a statement about the future of the restrictions which prevent aliens resident in this country from earning their living.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-bfd04c1e-a02a-4d3b-a5e0-6237a1203860" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-05-20/debates/67474fbf-3ef4-4bab-8db5-4636ce46ab04/Aliens#contribution-bfd04c1e-a02a-4d3b-a5e0-6237a1203860">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-be13978f-71d6-47a2-bbde-c4280a2c7442">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-be13978f-71d6-47a2-bbde-c4280a2c7442">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-be13978f-71d6-47a2-bbde-c4280a2c7442">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-be13978f-71d6-47a2-bbde-c4280a2c7442">
                Mr. Ness Edwards
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-be13978f-71d6-47a2-bbde-c4280a2c7442" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-05-20/debates/67474fbf-3ef4-4bab-8db5-4636ce46ab04/Aliens#contribution-be13978f-71d6-47a2-bbde-c4280a2c7442">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I am not clear what restrictions my hon. Friend has in mind. It is necessary, in the interests of British workers, to exercise a certain measure of control over the employment which may be taken by aliens, but I cannot admit that <span id="2185" class="column-number" data-column-number="2185"></span> this control has the result suggested in the Question in the case of aliens who are permitted to enter or to remain in this country for the purpose of engaging in employment. If my hon. Friend has any specific cases in mind and will send me particulars I shall he glad to look into them.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-be13978f-71d6-47a2-bbde-c4280a2c7442" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-05-20/debates/67474fbf-3ef4-4bab-8db5-4636ce46ab04/Aliens#contribution-be13978f-71d6-47a2-bbde-c4280a2c7442">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-42079131-2640-45a0-b84e-c0d7827e5355">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-42079131-2640-45a0-b84e-c0d7827e5355">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-42079131-2640-45a0-b84e-c0d7827e5355">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-42079131-2640-45a0-b84e-c0d7827e5355">
                Mr. Silverman
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-42079131-2640-45a0-b84e-c0d7827e5355" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-05-20/debates/67474fbf-3ef4-4bab-8db5-4636ce46ab04/Aliens#contribution-42079131-2640-45a0-b84e-c0d7827e5355">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Is not my hon. Friend aware that large numbers of aliens arc in this country and have been in this country for many years with a specific restriction endorsed on their visas that they are allowed to remain only so long as they refrain from entering into gainful employment, and is it not ridiculous that we should be scouring Europe for aliens to come here to work while there are thousands here already who are only too anxious to earn their own living and many of whom are prosecuted and imprisoned for doing so?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-42079131-2640-45a0-b84e-c0d7827e5355" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-05-20/debates/67474fbf-3ef4-4bab-8db5-4636ce46ab04/Aliens#contribution-42079131-2640-45a0-b84e-c0d7827e5355">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-65ceb978-df9c-4279-bc9c-da863fd55485">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-65ceb978-df9c-4279-bc9c-da863fd55485">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-65ceb978-df9c-4279-bc9c-da863fd55485">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-65ceb978-df9c-4279-bc9c-da863fd55485">
                Mr. Ness Edwards
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-65ceb978-df9c-4279-bc9c-da863fd55485" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-05-20/debates/67474fbf-3ef4-4bab-8db5-4636ce46ab04/Aliens#contribution-65ceb978-df9c-4279-bc9c-da863fd55485">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I do not think it right that an alien who comes into this country on compassionate grounds should then seek to gatecrash into employment.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-65ceb978-df9c-4279-bc9c-da863fd55485" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-05-20/debates/67474fbf-3ef4-4bab-8db5-4636ce46ab04/Aliens#contribution-65ceb978-df9c-4279-bc9c-da863fd55485">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-1f7e5ebd-f671-4216-b78c-80f4c3ab3d25">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-1f7e5ebd-f671-4216-b78c-80f4c3ab3d25">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-1f7e5ebd-f671-4216-b78c-80f4c3ab3d25">
